  $
  "CV" = s/overline(x) times 100%
  $

  $
  "CV"_"消費" &= 866337.74/1147824.06 &times 100% &≒ 75.48% \
  "CV"_"儲蓄" &= 197554.72/271158.16 &times 100% &≒ 72.86%
